      <title>Growtheum 向菲律宾冷藏连锁店投资 1.21 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/growtheum-to-invest-121-million-in-philippine-cold-chain-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Growtheum Capital Partners 将向菲律宾冷藏供应商 Mets Logistics Inc. 投资 70 亿比索（1.21 亿美元），支持该东南亚国家视为确保食品供应关键的行业。]]></description>
